# MediaPipe Model Directory

Download the pose landmarker model and place it here:

File: pose_landmarker_full.task

Download URL:
https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_full/float16/latest/pose_landmarker_full.task

Alternative models:
- Lite (faster, less accurate):
  https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_lite/float16/latest/pose_landmarker_lite.task

- Heavy (slower, more accurate) — NOT bundled in release (F8 on-demand via PoseLandmarkerHeavyModelStore):
  https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_heavy/float16/latest/pose_landmarker_heavy.task
  Debug: place pose_landmarker_heavy.task in src/debug/assets/ for offline dev.
